title: Imprint
---
body:

> **Translation notice.** This is a courtesy English translation of the German *Impressum*. The legally binding version is the German original at [pysv.org/imprint/](https://pysv.org/imprint/). In case of any discrepancy or legal dispute, the German version prevails.

This website is operated by Python Software Verband e.V.

