## Disclaimer

Despite careful review of the content, Python Software Verband e.V. accepts no liability or guarantee for the timeliness, accuracy, or completeness of the information on this website. The operators of linked websites are solely responsible for their content. Contributors are themselves responsible for the content they submit to participant pages.

This website contains links to websites operated by third parties. Python Software Verband e.V. has no control over such websites or the information, goods, or services offered there. Python Software Verband e.V. therefore assumes no responsibility, on any legal basis whatsoever, for the content of third-party websites.

Python Software Verband e.V. reserves the right to modify or update the information offered on this website at any time and without prior notice.

For any current or future legal relationships, German law applies exclusively, and only German courts have jurisdiction.
